{
  "uid": "v12-0-git-sync",
  "title": "Grafana 12.0 / 12.4 \u2014 Git Sync",
  "description": "Git Sync \u2014 experimental in OSS since 12.0, public preview in 12.4. Gated by the `gitSync` + `provisioning` feature toggles (both on in this lab). This dashboard links to the management UI + exposes the underlying API for smoke checks.",
