      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1.2rem;background:#1a2a3a;border-left:4px solid #5794f2;border-radius:6px;font-family:system-ui\"><div style=\"font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.18em;color:#8aa9d0;margin-bottom:.3rem\">DEMO GUIDE</div><div style=\"font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.6rem\">Grafana 12.0 / 12.4 \u2014 Git Sync</div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem\"><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#5794f2;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83c\udfaf What you're looking at</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Git Sync (experimental in 12.0, public preview in 12.4) lets you manage dashboards through a Git repo with PR review. Every save can land as a branch + PR.</div></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#73bf69;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83e\uddea Try this</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Open /admin/provisioning to register a repo, then save any dashboard \u2014 the Save drawer shows a branch selector.</div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:.8rem;padding-top:.6rem;border-top:1px solid #2d3e54;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udcda <strong style=\"color:#fff\">Learn more</strong>: <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/administration/provisioning/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Grafana docs</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/whatsnew/whats-new-in-v12-4/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">v12 What's New</a></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 11,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Git Sync \u2014 what it gives you\n\n| Feature | Where |\n|---|---|\n| Manage repos | [/admin/provisioning](/admin/provisioning) |\n| Repository CRD | `GET /apis/provisioning.grafana.app/v0alpha1/namespaces/default/repositories` |\n| Save drawer branch selector | Any dashboard \u2192 Save |\n| Sync status | [/admin/provisioning](/admin/provisioning) \u2192 repo \u2192 History |\n\n### Auth options (12.4)\n\n- **GitHub App** (preferred) \u2014 scoped to a single repo, webhook-driven.\n- **PAT** \u2014 fallback for dev, keep the scope narrow.\n\n### CI gate pattern\n\nEvery PR against the dashboards repo should run:\n\n1. JSON schema validation\n2. Headless render diff against staging\n3. Merge only if both pass\n\nSee [`ci/github-actions/gitsync-pr-check.yml`](https://github.com/gpadidala/grafana12-oss/blob/main/ci/github-actions/gitsync-pr-check.yml) in the repo."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "gitSync feature toggle",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "grafana_feature_toggle_info{name=\"gitSync\"} or on() vector(1)"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
